'''Daniel Hu<U+0148>a''' (born 25 June 1979) is a professional [[Czech Republic|Czech]] [[football (soccer)|football]]
player. He currently plays for [[FK Bohemians Prague (St<U+0159><U+00ED><U+017E>kov)]] on loan from [[1. FK P<U+0159><U+00ED>bram]].

After six and a half years at P<U+0159><U+00ED>bram, where he was captain, he joined [[FK Bohemians Praha (St<U+0159><U+00ED><U+017E>kov)]] on loan in June 2011.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://fotbal.idnes.cz/stari-vyhrali-i-bez-byvaleho-kapitana-huni-fj3-/fotbal.asp?c=A110621_134310_fotbal_mah |title=Sta<U+0159><U+00ED> vyhr<U+00E1>li i bez b<U+00FD>val<U+00E9>ho kapit<U+00E1>na Huni |publisher=idnes.cz |date=21 June 2011 |accessdate=4 July 2011}}{{cs icon}}</ref>

